    • Guest

      public Guest(String identity, String payment_id, int room_num, String name, String credit_card_number, String billing_address, String contact, String country, Gender gender, String nationality, String check_in_date)
      Create guest object, used when initializing from DB.
      Parameters:
      identity - Either national identity or driving license information
      payment_id - Filled when bill has been generated
      room_num - Filled when guest has checked in
      name - Name of Guest
      credit_card_number - Payment details
      billing_address - Address to send bill to
      contact - Mobile contact number
      country - Guest's country of origin
      gender - Gender of guest
      nationality - Nationality of guest
      check_in_date - Filled when guest has checked in, used for calculating days of stay automatically.
